~ start
Guardian: A hunter? A boat? A fire? No, those are three tortoises, on their slow journey across the heavens.
Guardian: One of them is lost. See? Over here.
Guardian: This one has forgotten its song. Without it, it cannot find the path back to the stars. You must help it remember.
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
